00:13:32.344 --> 00:13:35.213
and provide training,
courses, and workshops.

00:13:35.213 --> 00:13:39.117
The next ones aligned is one
with the prosecutor's office

00:13:39.117 --> 00:13:41.319
from SÃ£o Paulo
where they rely on

00:13:41.319 --> 00:13:43.288
international
prosecutor's task force

00:13:43.288 --> 00:13:45.557
against wildlife
trafficking in Brazil.

00:13:45.557 --> 00:13:47.559
We will bring South
American prosecutors

00:13:47.559 --> 00:13:50.061
to develop international
agreements on how we can

00:13:50.061 --> 00:13:53.632
better cooperate against
wildlife trafficking regionally

00:13:53.632 --> 00:13:56.134
and how we can join
the global efforts.

00:13:56.134 --> 00:13:58.537
We also have an aligned workshop

00:13:58.537 --> 00:14:00.205
with the Brazilian
