00:14:02.607 --> 00:14:05.477
Lastly, we are
producing with SOS Fauna

00:14:05.477 --> 00:14:08.346
post-seizure procedure
guides on how to

00:14:08.346 --> 00:14:12.384
radically decrease the death
rate post after the animals are

00:14:12.384 --> 00:14:14.019
seized by law enforcement

00:14:14.019 --> 00:14:17.790
by taking very simple
and cheap measures like

00:14:17.790 --> 00:14:22.060
this animal likes cold and
this animal hates heat, etc.

00:14:22.060 --> 00:14:24.129
But that's not enough!

00:14:24.129 --> 00:14:26.565
My next goal is to get
involved with efforts

00:14:26.565 --> 00:14:29.200
to change the Brazilian
environmental legislation

00:14:29.200 --> 00:14:32.738
and try to encompass wildlife
trafficking as a full crime

00:14:32.738 --> 00:14:35.473
because believe it
or not, it doesn't.

00:14:35.473 --> 00:14:38.309
If your country's legislation
is anything like ours,

00:14:38.309 --> 00:14:40.312
tell your law makers
you want to change it

00:14:40.312 --> 00:14:42.982
and encompass wildlife
trafficking as a full crime

00:14:42.982 --> 00:14:45.184
as it is a crime
against humanity.

00:14:47.920 --> 00:14:50.389
These animals are
being withdrawn

00:14:50.389 --> 00:14:52.524
from the environment
on a regular basis

00:14:52.524 --> 00:14:54.726
to be people's pets.

00:14:54.726 --> 00:14:57.295
Should we maintain
the so-called cultural habit

00:14:57.295 --> 00:14:59.465
just because we are used to it?

00:15:00.999 --> 00:15:04.703
If commercial captive
breeding of wild animals

00:15:04.703 --> 00:15:06.971
makes law enforcement
and protecting

00:15:06.971 --> 00:15:09.174
our biodiversity more difficult,

00:15:09.174 --> 00:15:12.477
should we do this
just so that some people

00:15:12.477 --> 00:15:16.481
can fulfill their desire
of owning a wild animal?

00:15:16.481 --> 00:15:19.317
If we fail, consequences
may be severe

00:15:19.317 --> 00:15:21.252
and even not fixable.

00:15:21.252 --> 00:15:24.323
Cultures are dynamic
and can and must evolve.

00:15:24.323 --> 00:15:25.991
So I'd say no!

00:15:25.991 --> 00:15:28.994
These animals in
all endless forms

00:15:28.994 --> 00:15:31.063
most beautiful
and most wonderful

00:15:31.063 --> 00:15:34.299
should be out in a healthy
and dynamic environment

00:15:34.299 --> 00:15:36.301
fulfilling their
ecological roles

00:15:36.301 --> 00:15:38.070
and their evolutionary roles

00:15:38.070 --> 00:15:39.771
as species that
evolve over time.

00:15:39.771 --> 00:15:41.206
Thank you.

